  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "OPAL coupling. Alien formant with high tilt — the upper partials dominate and OPAL's granular FM scatters them into prismatic sprays of inharmonic color. The result is not a voice but a spectral dust cloud that retains the memory of vocal formant shapes. Bright, crystalline, and entirely alien. Each grain is a splinter of a vowel.",
